# Knockout 2026 — Codebase Analysis

## Overview

**Knockout 2026** is a custom **WordPress** theme for a premium sports café/entertainment lounge located in **Kolkata, India**. The site is hosted locally via **Laragon** at `c:\laragon\www\Knockout-2026`. The theme is called `KNOCKOUT2026` (internally "Sports Cafe Theme") and is authored by *Muhammad Junaid*.

> [!NOTE]
> The project is a **pure WordPress/PHP theme** — no React, Next.js, or build tooling is involved (despite conversation history referencing React components, those were removed or are from a separate layer).

---

