## Theme Structure

### Core Files

| File | Size | Purpose |
|------|------|---------|
| [functions.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/functions.php) | 335 lines | Theme setup, asset enqueuing, auto-page creation, widget areas, menus, body classes |
| [header.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/header.php) | 92 lines | Glassmorphism header with neon particles canvas, nav, WhatsApp/Call CTAs, mobile toggle |
| [footer.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/footer.php) | 106 lines | 4-column grid footer (about, explore, experiences, contact), mouse trail effect |
| [front-page.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/front-page.php) | 447 lines | Homepage with video showcase, hero, Why Choose Us, services, and more |
| [style.css](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/style.css) | 12 lines | Theme metadata only — actual styles loaded from `assets/css/` |

---

### Includes (`inc/`)

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| [custom-post-types.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/inc/custom-post-types.php) | Registers 3 CPTs (`food_menu`, `events`, `live_matches`) and 3 taxonomies (`menu_category`, `event_type`, `sport_type`) |
| [acf-fields.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/inc/acf-fields.php) | ACF field groups for menu items (price, spicy, gluten-free, vegetarian), events (date, time, cover, featured), matches (teams, date, time, channel, live status) |
| [enqueue-scripts.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/inc/enqueue-scripts.php) | **Legacy/duplicate** `wp_enqueue_scripts` — superseded by `functions.php` |
| [theme-setup.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/inc/theme-setup.php) | Theme support setup |
| [customizer.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Knockout-2026/wp-content/themes/KNOCKOUT2026/inc/customizer.php) | Customizer options (empty) |

> [!WARNING]
> `inc/enqueue-scripts.php` duplicates the asset enqueuing already handled in `functions.php` with different handle names (`sports-cafe-*` vs `knockout-*`). These may conflict if both are active.

