## Design System

The theme uses a **dark premium aesthetic** with neon accents:

| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `--black` | `#000000` | Primary background |
| `--neon` / `--neon-green` | `#b0d136` | Accent color throughout |
| `--neon-glow` | `rgba(176, 209, 54, 0.5)` | Glow/shadow effects |
| `--gradient-1` | Gold (`#ffd700`) | Gradient text |
| `--gradient-2` | Cyan (`#00ffff`) | Gradient text |
| Font primary | `Roboto` | Body text |
| Font display | `Alphacorsa Personal Use` | Logo/display headings |

**Key visual effects:**
- Glassmorphism (`backdrop-filter: blur`) on header and cards
- Neon glow text shadows and pulsing animations
- Canvas-based particle background
- Mouse trail effect (footer.php inline script)
- Scroll-triggered fade-in/slide-up animations

