## Custom Post Types & Taxonomies

```mermaid
graph LR
    FM["food_menu CPT"] --> MC["menu_category (taxonomy)"]
    EV["events CPT"] --> ET["event_type (taxonomy)"]
    LM["live_matches CPT"] --> ST["sport_type (taxonomy)"]
```

Each CPT has ACF field groups for structured data entry (prices, dates, times, etc.).

